      • getSummary

        ContactTrackingSummaryReport getSummary(String contactId,
                                      String createdSinceTimestamp)
                                        throws ConstantContactServiceException
        Implements the get Summary operation of the Contact Tracking API by calling the ConstantContact server side.
        Parameters:
        contactId - The id of the contact.
        createdSinceTimestamp - This time stamp is an ISO-8601 ordinal date supporting offset.
        It will return only the summary since the supplied date.
        If you want to bypass this filter, set createdSinceTimestamp to null.
        Returns:
        The ContactTrackingSummaryReport containing data returned by the server on success;
        An exception is thrown otherwise.
        Throws:
        ConstantContactServiceException - When something went wrong in the Constant Contact flow or an error is returned from server.
